@node "Chrace" "Choosing a race"


  There are many intelligent humanoid races in IOT, some of which you
 can choose to control as a character. Each race has different statistics
 and abilities due to their racial background and culture.

  Choose wisely, as the only way you can change races is by dying, and
 rolling up a new character. Unless you survive so long that you end up
 old and decrepit or something.. I'd let you change then. :)

  The following applies though; Only Humans, Hill Dwarves, Elves and
 Dwarves are widely accepted as factual by the Human population of
 Tharthaal. In fact, many Humans don't even believe in Elves. You must
 always think about this when playing, as people are often afraid of the
 unknown.


